Package model.calendar

Class Lesson

java.lang.Object
model.calendar.Lesson
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Lesson extends Object implements Serializable
This class is a representation of a lesson that contains information on which course it is, the teacher teaching the lesson, the date, start and end time and the room(s) it is held in. It implements Serializable interface for persistence purposes.
